  <h2>Types of appointment</h2>
  <p>We offer:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Telephone consultations</strong> — a clinician will call you at an agreed time</li>
    <li><strong>Face-to-face appointments</strong> — at Cameron Health Centre in Methil</li>
    <li><strong>On-the-day appointments</strong> — for urgent same-day needs, call us from 08:00</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Who will I see?</h2>
  <p>Depending on your needs, you may be offered an appointment with:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>A GP</li>
    <li>A practice nurse or advanced nurse practitioner</li>
    <li>A pharmacist</li>
    <li>A physiotherapist (if applicable)</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Our reception team are trained to ask a few questions to help match you to the right clinician.</p>

  <h2>Need help sooner?</h2>
  <p>Many conditions can be treated faster without a GP appointment. Consider:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/get-help/pharmacy-first/">Pharmacy First</a> — for UTIs, earache, sinusitis, sore throat, and more</li>
    <li><a href="/get-help/self-referral/">Self-referral services</a> — direct access to physiotherapy, mental health, and more</li>
  </ul>

